{"tid":2315141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波稱香港金融體系穩如泰山   拒評論許智峯戶口凍結事件","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T04:50:27.000Z","uid":46356,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4c213a253e8dc2761f69246390dbe23c25cf09b0","tid":2315141,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:27:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415646&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=e3ab8847\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415646&h=07c00eba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=415646</a><br />\n<br />\n陳茂波：指控許智峯戶口被凍結因部門出錯純粹臆測<br />\n1小時前<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波出席立法會財經事務委員會，被問到許智峯及家人戶口未經法庭批准下被凍結，有議員質疑有部門出錯，陳茂波認為指控是臆測，不會評論個別事件。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（新界西）鄭松泰：「警方有權力就洗黑錢、販毒等與銀行業務相關的案件，他們是有權暫時有凍結令，但無論如何也要經過原訟庭申請資產凍結令，突然解封一定意味有出錯，是否有部門下命令後程序出錯？在沒有任何司法基礎下進行抄家行為？」<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波：「鄭松泰議員的指控純粹憑臆測，我們不會就個別個案詳情在這裡進行討論，<span class=\"red\">至於香港金融中心的地位，自去年暴力事件到今年新冠疫情，到過去幾個月所謂制裁，我們經歷過十幾個月的挑戰，仍然穩如泰山</span>，我覺得鄭松泰議員的提問不需要再處理。」"},{"pid":"955943f48ba9ac216e909476cf477c64a38301d7","tid":2315141,"uid":266342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"通常嗰啲支那族講埋晒呢啲咁嘅說話<br />\n就代表佢哋好心虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d5ac2b7b014e294d09b58782643bb01bc5e815","tid":2315141,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"但無論如何也要經過原訟庭申請資產凍結令<br />\n11哥話銀行可以選擇配合驚方 唔一定要向法庭申請"},{"pid":"f41fa87c4b63c7d7c022c70848a6de145b8948c9","tid":2315141,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}